data.description: BACK ON MARKET AFTER UPGRADES (new flooring, including luxury vinyl in living areas and wet areas, and carpet upstairs; new paint inside and out!). Great Townhome, Great Location! This 3/2.5 townhome includes these upgrades: New ROOF 2020, New Water Heater 2020, New A/C 2016.  Also includes all appliances (incl. washer/dryer), an upstairs living area/playroom, under stairs storage, security system, natural backyard area, and lots of windows. This unit is also close to the community pool and playground. Minutes from interstates, restaurants, shopping, and more!  Come take a tour!
